The "lat1-12-vt" font has been removed from VTJ-1 because it may be
under the GPL (GNU General Public License).  You may still use it
with VTJ-1 by installing the source font running the mapping script
(vtj1fonter.tcl) yourself.  If you do so, it is up to you to comply
with the license terms.

